{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/sapporo-snow-festival-festival-salju-terbesar-di-jepang/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"“Sapporo Snow Festival” Festival Salju Terbesar di Jepang","content":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Festival musim dingin terbesar di Jepang bernama Sapporo Snow Festival sudah dibuka lho. Sapporo Snow Festival yang ke 69 ini berlangsung di kota Sapporo, Hokaido yang diselenggarakan pada minggu pertama di bulan Februari.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_43018\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-43018\" data-attachment-id=\"43018\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/sapporo-snow-festival-festival-salju-terbesar-di-jepang/attachment/2-246/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/2-2.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"(Source : Facebook @WelcomeSapporo)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;(Source : Facebook @WelcomeSapporo)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/2-2-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/2-2.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-43018\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/2-2.jpg\" alt=\"(Source : Facebook @WelcomeSapporo)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/2-2.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/2-2-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-43018\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">(Source : Facebook @WelcomeSapporo)</p></div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Festival terbesar musim dingin ini pertama kali diselenggarakan oleh Dinas Pariwisata Sapporo dan pemerintah kota Sapporo, dengan sponsor dari surat kabar lokal <em>Hokkai Times</em> pada tahun 1950. Sebelumnya pernah dilangsungkan berbagai festival salju di kota Sapporo, namun terhenti saat Perang Dunia II. Ide membuat patung dari salju ini diambil dari festival salju yang diadakan tahun 1935 oleh murid-murid sebuah SD di kota Otaru.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sapporo Snow Festival bermula dari sekumpulan siswa SMP dan SMA di Sapporo yang meletakkan 6 buah patung salju hasil karya mereka di tengah Odori Park. Sejak itu, dimulailah pameran patung-patung salju, permainan perang bola salju, dan juga karnaval. Dari itu semua, lahirlah Sapporo Snow Festival yang diselenggakan hingga kini.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_43022\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-43022\" data-attachment-id=\"43022\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/sapporo-snow-festival-festival-salju-terbesar-di-jepang/attachment/6-202/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/6-1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"(Source : Facebook @WelcomeSapporo)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;(Source : Facebook @WelcomeSapporo)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/6-1-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/6-1.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-43022\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/6-1.jpg\" alt=\"(Source : Facebook @WelcomeSapporo)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/6-1.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/6-1-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-43022\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">(Source : Facebook @WelcomeSapporo)</p></div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Pada festival ini terdapat lebih dari 200 patung salju dan es yang dipamerkan, termasuk 5 patung salju dan 2 patung es  setinggi 15 meter. Wah tinggi banget ya bro sis.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_43021\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-43021\" data-attachment-id=\"43021\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/sapporo-snow-festival-festival-salju-terbesar-di-jepang/attachment/5-261/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/5-2.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"(Source : twitter.com)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;(Source : twitter.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/5-2-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/5-2.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-43021\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/5-2.jpg\" alt=\"(Source : twitter.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/5-2.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/5-2-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-43021\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">(Source : twitter.com)</p></div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sejak tahun 2006 festival ini diadakan di 3 area dengan pameran berbeda di setiap areanya. Area-area tersebut adalah:</p>\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li><strong>Odori Park</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<div id=\"attachment_43020\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-43020\" data-attachment-id=\"43020\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/sapporo-snow-festival-festival-salju-terbesar-di-jepang/attachment/4-260/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/4-2.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"(Source : facebook.com)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;(Source : facebook.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/4-2-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/4-2.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-43020\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/4-2.jpg\" alt=\"(Source : facebook.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/4-2.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/4-2-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-43020\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">(Source : facebook.com)</p></div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Di Odori Park ini bro sis bisa melihat berbagai karya yang terbuat dari salju. Karya tersebut akan dipamerkan dari sisi timur sampai ke barat dari pusat kota Sapporo. Odori Park ini akan dibagi menjadi 12 <em>chrome</em> dimana patung salju yang indah akan di tampilkan. Area ini menjadi daya tarik terbesar pada Sapporo Snow Festival.</p>\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li><strong>Distrik Susukino</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<div id=\"attachment_43017\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-43017\" data-attachment-id=\"43017\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/sapporo-snow-festival-festival-salju-terbesar-di-jepang/attachment/1-305/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/1-2.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"(Source : Facebook @WelcomeSapporo)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;(Source : Facebook @WelcomeSapporo)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/1-2-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/1-2.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-43017\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/1-2.jpg\" alt=\"(Source : Facebook @WelcomeSapporo)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/1-2.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/1-2-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-43017\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">(Source : Facebook @WelcomeSapporo)</p></div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jika di Odori Park dipamerkan berbagai karya dari salju, maka di Susukino dipamerkan berbagai pahatan es. Dengan tema “<em>Enjoy the Ice”</em>, di sini akan ditampilkan lebih dari 60 pahatan es. Bro sis juga bisa berkunjung ke “Fureai Hiroba” untuk mencoba naik kendaraan dari pahatan es dan berfoto di “<em>Illumination Street</em>”.</p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong> </strong><strong style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">Tsudome </strong></li>\n</ul>\n<div id=\"attachment_43019\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-43019\" data-attachment-id=\"43019\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/sapporo-snow-festival-festival-salju-terbesar-di-jepang/attachment/3-270/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/3-2.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"(Source : Facebook @WelcomeSapporo)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;(Source : Facebook @WelcomeSapporo)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/3-2-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/3-2.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-43019\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/3-2.jpg\" alt=\"(Source : Facebook @WelcomeSapporo)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/3-2.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/3-2-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-43019\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">(Source : Facebook @WelcomeSapporo)</p></div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ternyata festival ini bukan hanya dijadikan sebagai tempat memamerkan hasil karya dari salju dan es aja lho. Tapi bro sis juga bisa bermain sepuasnya di berbagai permainan salju. Di area Tsudome ini tersedia berbagai permainan seperti <em>Tube Slider,</em> yang panjangnya 100 meter. <em>Snow Raft,</em> dimana bro sis bisa naik <em>rafting boat</em> yang ditarik oleh <em>snowmobile</em>. <em>Bumper Ball, </em>permainan dimana kita menggunakan <em>bumper ball air cushion</em> dan menggelindingkan di atas salju, dan masih banyak yang lainnya. Area Tsudome ini dibuka dari jam 9 pagi sampai 5 sore.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Seru bangetkan bro sis, festival ini merupakan cara lain untuk bisa menikmati musim dingin di Jepang dan tentunya sebagai sarana mengembangkan kreativitas juga lho. Bro sis yang punya rencana untuk pergi ke Jepang, jangan lupa untuk mampir Sapporo Snow Festival ini ya.</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"e0ccb860-77b2-5687-bdd8-fb88bd23574a"}}}